data.description: Welcome Home to an amazing colonial, in Gates Mills, that combines historic charm and modern updates. The main level offers convenience and versatility with incredible updates from an enormous eat-in kitchen with quartz countertops, rolling butchers block, updated cabinetry newer appliances, and a historic brick wall & mantle with wood burning fireplace and exposed wooden beams. A huge living room continues the exposed wood beams and new laminate floors, in addition to updated lighting, and framed entertainment wall for your TV above an electric fireplace. An Office / Bedroom with beautiful woodwork, built in shelves & cabinets, double closets & exterior door and updated full bath off the kitchen complete the main level. Ascend to the second floor where you’ll discover the incredible master suite with charming original wood floors, wood burning fireplace, and historic built-ins leading to a remodeled oversized closet, and master bathroom that has been overhauled to include a brick and tile shower with bench seating, all new dual sink vanity, lighting and more. Continue down the hall to find a third remodeled full bathroom accessed from the hall and large bedroom with built-ins and original wood floors, along with the newly added cozy fourth bedroom and fully equipped laundry room. A Wooded and private lot include a shed, fire-pit and brick patio. New Roof, Boiler/Furnace, custom baseboard covers, 2nd floor Laundry all installed 10/2023; Don’t wait see this amazing home today.
